{"tid":607154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賣假日本蜜瓜　店東罰款$6,000","createTime":"2018-03-27T05:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T09:52:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"b636660e5f6f6f126d18f9283d95509b48d9f8a1","tid":607154,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:24:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180327/20344231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F20344231&d=1i6%2BM0Kai%2BovlyjlPb85Jf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=67b097f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F20344231&h=2424ec66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180327/20344231</a><br />\n<br />\n賣假日本蜜瓜　店東罰款$6,000<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180327/large/27la5p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180327%2Flarge%2F27la5p11.jpg&h=cb1505b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n果販麥首忠昨認罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【海關首控】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】日本福岡甜王士多啤梨、香印提子、澳洲塔斯曼尼亞車厘子等貴價水果，不時有偽冒產地的平價貨魚目混珠，昨首見入罪案例。果販於深水埗兩店舖，以內地出產的平價蜜瓜冒充「日本北海道蜜瓜」，海關接報後放蛇，以每個25元購得蜜瓜，但店員無法出示產地證明。東主昨在西九龍法院承認違反《商品說明條例》，罰款6,000元，是海關首宗檢控假日本蜜瓜案件。<br />\n<br />\n報稱商人的被告麥首忠（50歲）承認兩項供應及兩項管有具虛假商品說明貨品罪，指他於今年1月23及24日在桂林街及大南街兩間地舖，出售共115個及存放65個假北海道蜜瓜，全部180個瓜總值4,500元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180327/large/a0805a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180327%2Flarge%2Fa0805a.gif&h=d813d7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求情稱「賣得好平」<br />\n<br />\n案情指，瓜上附有寫明「北海道」的紙條，價錢牌標示為「日本蜜瓜」，但調查發現被告從油麻地一家生果批發商入貨時，已明知原產地實為中國大陸。涉案兩舖店員指，被告指使她們推銷時宣稱是日本貨，但沒告知她們蜜瓜的真實產地是內地。<br />\n<br />\n被告有兩項呃秤及三項不同類案底，昨親自求情指非為牟取暴利，只想促銷，「已經賣得好平」。裁判官駁斥：「促銷都唔能夠咁樣，賣好平都咁話。咁人哋賣正貨嗰啲點？」裁判官就每罪判罰1,500元，並告誡被告「你自己做生意應該知要老實」，再犯未必再判罰款。控罪最高可判罰款500萬元及監禁5年。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者昨走訪涉案兩店，已不見有「北海道日本蜜瓜」，有售的唯一一款蜜瓜只標示為「蜜瓜」或「白蜜瓜」，瓜上貼紙稱產自墨西哥，每個標價20至25元。店員對查詢十分警惕，交談兩句便生疑：「你係咪海關嗰啲呀？海關成日嚟搞搞震，等我認住你個樣，睇吓你幾時起我底。」記者問產地是那裏時，其中一店的阿姐斬釘截鐵回答：「唔知！自己睇（標示）！我唔識睇。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC1367/18<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"56346b59f8edf3e009939b8f3a3ad732c7623413","tid":607154,"uid":12021,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd01b61010634d5434a320230357e2f1e17d1616","tid":607154,"uid":173397,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:35:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2359490d405c8adeb27137c4e9e4615c16b600b","tid":607154,"uid":13257,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:35:10.000Z","msg":"罰得咁輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd414d55c0a5c5ab836117006128e366ae329f4f","tid":607154,"uid":87540,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:36:39.000Z","msg":"你唔會買到依個級數，要專登訂先有"},{"pid":"3af5ad0961f85f94ac681e2fd8bbf842b94fd9a8","tid":607154,"uid":53037,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:37:29.000Z","msg":"啲店員仲咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c49855441299eb9012516b2bd1c1d0f98e7ae42","tid":607154,"uid":26332,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:38:16.000Z","msg":"仆街低賤人口就係呢啲<br />\n罰得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81e02df73fd478e722519ff6fb49a53a5db0b40","tid":607154,"uid":103317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"賣咁平一睇就知係特秀級only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07db9eacd35bf740145beff7799dcaea10e9d89b","tid":607154,"uid":3454,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:38:37.000Z","msg":"上環有日本人開左間生果飲品舖"},{"pid":"17e617825b9ef7b1855cce06a462bd4e60bbea2a","tid":607154,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:38:39.000Z","msg":"有冇菠蘿包冇菠蘿嘅朋友出黎講幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc5ae29003ddf5bfb1379645b388c63644e0e55","tid":607154,"uid":158755,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd01b61010634d5434a320230357e2f1e17d1616","tid":607154,"uid":173397,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:35:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c1d97dc1b2c3cf61155b8bfadc422a2612ae99","tid":607154,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3af5ad0961f85f94ac681e2fd8bbf842b94fd9a8","tid":607154,"uid":53037,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:37:29.000Z","msg":"啲店員仲咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:39:59.000Z","msg":"成班都係黑社會梗係串"},{"pid":"f29f509aae7d4b640de4ec47da5180a3d5d3b1e7","tid":607154,"uid":26168,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"香港d 聲稱日本士多啤梨不嬲全撚部都假，<br />\n喺日本食過的話無可能食唔出，根本兩樣嘢黎，喺香港中過一次伏之後絕對唔會再買"},{"pid":"8ac158f733e96fb7cfa0ec00ce8dae597d823fe0","tid":607154,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f030c56885fd1036e2319a1edfdff95de22952a3","tid":607154,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"賣多幾個又回本"},{"pid":"51154299d425e603a8d06e4416a8f875d55ea11e","tid":607154,"uid":